Submitted December 20, 2010, reversed and remanded March 23, 2011 GERALD LEE BYRNS, Petitioner, v. BOARD OF PAROLE AND POST-PRISON SUPERVISION, Respondent.

Board of Parole and Post-Prison Supervision

A142800 249 P3d 1290 Peter Gartlan, Chief Defender, Zachary Lovett Mazer, Deputy Public Defender, and Office of Public Defense Services, filed the brief for appellant. John R. Kroger, Attorney General, David B. Thompson, Interim Solicitor General, and Jeff J. Payne, Assistant Attorney General, filed the brief for respondent. Before Brewer, Chief Judge, and Gillette, Senior Judge. PER CURIAM

Reversed and remanded. Janowski /Fleming v. Board of Parole, 349 Or 432, 245 P3d 1270 (2010).
